<h1>Messenger</h1>
<p>Greetings <%= @user.name %>!</p>
<br>
<p>Here is a link to reset your password: <%= link_to "Reset password", edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email), class: "btn btn-primary btn-block mt-1" %> </p>
<p>Note that this link will <strong>expire in two hours.</strong></p>
<p>If you didn't request this reset link, you can safely delete and disregard this email.</p>
<br>

